{"tid":169812,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵私補","createTime":"2017-03-24T11:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T12:32:45.000Z","uid":94461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4901ebc2e735e8f353e8b27365cb78c2f837ac66","tid":169812,"uid":94461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"就黎考DSE，依家先識得黎驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知太遲，各位唔好屌得太大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n窮撚一個，比唔到太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係想搵一個教到我野，因為DSE殺到，希望認真對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想搵補英文同數學既 最好兩樣一齊教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為時間難就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有意tg我 <a href=\"https://t.me/onl799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fonl799&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=bbafef28\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/onl799</a>"},{"pid":"d841ef8844e1e8b615ecb6a56861ee0a8ea4d5e7","tid":169812,"uid":24063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:55:45.000Z","msg":"今年dse...?"},{"pid":"79018bbeb06db611089e9bb2e12254af64fe25a7","tid":169812,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"太早啦 未係時間溫書"},{"pid":"d9ccb7a4056f9e17e0b80f942d142d2385898c8e","tid":169812,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"下年大把時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf02e20ce0fb83b16b98686f2f39125785c9ee8","tid":169812,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:00:18.000Z","msg":"而家先溫 俾埋答案你都記唔切啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd05caa0f872f3a00121ccb936fb375fbc87a114","tid":169812,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:04:14.000Z","msg":"仲有成年時間邊會遲"},{"pid":"96b7367a368f82a976508279b6f602a476caa38f","tid":169812,"uid":94461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知衰喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46bcd1e7f83eb7affb2c4717699bed496f8fa54","tid":169812,"uid":13317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好咁啦各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知衰喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想幫你 不過唔知點幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然英數兩科都補得 但你時間無多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d322858975fc24393619994ce2676ab645e53771","tid":169812,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"又冇時間又冇錢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明年請早"},{"pid":"4845b83c6d795d1c86033652558188d3be3ef665","tid":169812,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"時間又無錢又無 穩鬼補"},{"pid":"8bf3d0f20c9e435169c460bc905406e15a8811bd","tid":169812,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"知衰就下年再黎啦 咁短時間可以追得返既話你根本唔使靠人 如果唔得既話搵黎都哂氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afe2ebb39718ac212b49d0109b02658c08eea56","tid":169812,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"畀唔到太多 仲想補兩科主科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要話時間難就<br />\n而加唔洗返學有幾難就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心態又無 死到臨頭先搵人幫你<br />\n<br />\n如果你係窮又有心補 早啲開聲我肯定你起呢到搵到人平平地幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a908ff11ac53cc04ead0abfab8bc132cbb170a","tid":169812,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"你係靚女另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ddec9435168758a5e581661e3e81045f9315f1","tid":169812,"uid":91502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"如果你aim攞2既 可以平平地幫你"},{"pid":"b2e22ba4ffba1b0cd417b4f32e2db06954b160e2","tid":169812,"uid":38955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"樓主tg有相喎 巴打們可以狗衝"}]}